The paper deals with the problem of sanitizing sensitive patterns in string data while preserving data utility. This problem is relevant to several areas of computer science, including data structures (cs.DS), cryptography and security (cs.CR), databases (cs.DB), machine learning (cs.LG), and information theory (cs.IT). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
